program today along with gov john sununu of new hampshire whom 
bush recently named as his new chief of staff and former bush 
campaign manager lee atwater whom bush has recommended to be 
chairman of the republican national committee 
the presidentelect is to meet with the governors tuesday 
castle said the lineup of influential bush staff members and the 
presidentelect put the conference as much in the forefront of 
changing events as any such meeting could be 
i think this administration in washington is going to be even 
more sensitive to the states said missouri gov john ashcroft 
