here just laugh when i say im retired elion said i do like to 
stay busy 
whats the use of retiring if you dont have anything to 
contribute any more people will tell you but as long as you can 
make a contribution you should science is a continuum if the 
older ones dont pass along their knowledge to the younger ones it 
comes to a dead stop 
