jobs since 1982 the report said california was in the lead with 
228900 followed by michigan with 114500 in the last two years 
however michigan has lost 66000 manufacturing jobs the board said 
also gaining manufacturing jobs since 1982 were north carolina 
91400 florida 90600 indiana 78600 georgia 78300 and 
minnesota 55400 
